DESCRIPTION:Join us for an engaging exploration of your ward's urban landscape! In this interactive session\, participants will dive into the world of local climate action\, discussing everything from water and energy to mobility and waste. Through lively group activities and role-playing\, you will reflect on what makes these systems thrive\, identify vulnerabilities\, and brainstorm creative solutions. \n\nTogether\, you will design a hands-on action plan for your chosen system\, turning challenges into exciting opportunities for community collaboration and a brighter\, more sustainable future for the city!\n\nFacilitated by Ujjvala Krishna and Dr Manan Bhan as part of their project Heat in Bangalore at ATREE.\n\nLink for registration: https://forms.gle/PY7BYHBUWLsddXKm6
